{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/travel/2020/07/31/夜郎谷一个臆想出来的景区.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"5dd2c403-e660-5a70-9f33-1068496c1f91","excerpt":"…","html":"<h1>夜郎谷一个臆想出来的景区</h1>\n<p>夜郎国是大概西汉时期位于贵州的小国，史记有记载夜郎自大的典故，贵州省博其实就一个展牌有介绍夜郎国，估计除了史记也没什么实际的考古发现来证明它。不过没关系，一个美术家，宋培伦通过二十年直接在贵阳大学城做了个假的夜郎国遗址。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/37da94db2221fbdac52cf107fdeff880/4b190/2020-07-31-0.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/37da94db2221fbdac52cf107fdeff880/cbe2e/2020-07-31-0.webp 148w,\n/static/37da94db2221fbdac52cf107fdeff880/3084c/2020-07-31-0.webp 295w,\n/static/37da94db2221fbdac52cf107fdeff880/5ca24/2020-07-31-0.webp 590w,\n/static/37da94db2221fbdac52cf107fdeff880/d00b9/2020-07-31-0.webp 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/37da94db2221fbdac52cf107fdeff880/a80bd/2020-07-31-0.jpg 148w,\n/static/37da94db2221fbdac52cf107fdeff880/1c91a/2020-07-31-0.jpg 295w,\n/static/37da94db2221fbdac52cf107fdeff880/1c72d/2020-07-31-0.jpg 590w,\n/static/37da94db2221fbdac52cf107fdeff880/4b190/2020-07-31-0.jpg 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/37da94db2221fbdac52cf107fdeff880/1c72d/2020-07-31-0.jpg\"\n          alt=\"夜郎谷\"\n          title=\"夜郎谷\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">夜郎谷</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>前往夜郎谷并不容易，整个贵阳大学城在贵阳的最南端，是个完全鸟不拉屎的地方，因为重要的交通枢纽都在北方，前往夜郎谷至少要转两班公交大概两个小时车程才能到。</p>\n<p>尽管旅程很长，但是夜郎谷绝对值得一看。话说毕竟是艺术家，相比于长沙的万家丽，这个夜郎谷虽说没什么依据，审美上是完全超群的。迎合疫情，柱状人面都带上了口罩。话说整个景区有一种隐约的性隐喻。穿过一群人面石柱，藏着一个悬崖，崖面有一个裂缝，裂缝里面是一个溶洞可以走到山坡顶。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8e24b0f5302734de6d484cc08e9d6df5/4b190/2020-07-31.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/8e24b0f5302734de6d484cc08e9d6df5/cbe2e/2020-07-31.webp 148w,\n/static/8e24b0f5302734de6d484cc08e9d6df5/3084c/2020-07-31.webp 295w,\n/static/8e24b0f5302734de6d484cc08e9d6df5/5ca24/2020-07-31.webp 590w,\n/static/8e24b0f5302734de6d484cc08e9d6df5/d00b9/2020-07-31.webp 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/8e24b0f5302734de6d484cc08e9d6df5/a80bd/2020-07-31.jpg 148w,\n/static/8e24b0f5302734de6d484cc08e9d6df5/1c91a/2020-07-31.jpg 295w,\n/static/8e24b0f5302734de6d484cc08e9d6df5/1c72d/2020-07-31.jpg 590w,\n/static/8e24b0f5302734de6d484cc08e9d6df5/4b190/2020-07-31.jpg 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/8e24b0f5302734de6d484cc08e9d6df5/1c72d/2020-07-31.jpg\"\n          alt=\"合个影也是很开心的体验\"\n          title=\"合个影也是很开心的体验\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">合个影也是很开心的体验</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>个人感觉，如果在贵阳，这个景区是绝对值得去的，何况现在还是免费的~</p>","frontmatter":{"category":"travel"},"fields":{"slug":"/travel/2020/07/31/夜郎谷一个臆想出来的景区.html","date":"July 31, 2020","title":"夜郎谷一个臆想出来的景区"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/travel/2020/07/31/夜郎谷一个臆想出来的景区.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/travel/2020/07/29/黔灵山公园看猴子.html","title":"黔灵山公园看猴子"},"frontmatter":{"category":"travel"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/travel/2020/08/03/安顺龙宫.html","title":"安顺龙宫"},"frontmatter":{"category":"travel"}}}}}